<paragraph id="8B8DFB56FFD17F6AFF1CF7EEFE57B4CC" blockId="9.[136,1452,482,1589]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFF1CF7EEFE9EB780" bold="true" box="[136,261,482,508]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFEB5F7EEFE76B780" authorityName="Lansdown &amp; Hassemer" authorityYear="2021" box="[289,493,482,508]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ciliata">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFEB5F7EEFE76B780" box="[289,493,482,508]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Callitriche ciliata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from all other 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFD6FF7EEFC4AB780" box="[763,977,482,508]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFD6FF7EEFCEFB780" box="[763,884,482,508]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Callitriche</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
apart from 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFBF5F7EFFEE5B45C" authority="Schotsman (1967: 39)" authorityName="Schotsman" authorityPageNumber="39" authorityYear="1967" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="truncata" subSpecies="fimbriata">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFBF5F7EFFB7EB780" box="[1121,1253,483,509]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">C. truncata</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFAD7F7EEFA30B780" box="[1347,1451,482,508]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">fimbriata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFA386A7FFD17F6AFF1CF40AFEE5B45C" author="Schotsman, H. D." box="[136,382,518,544]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" refId="ref31122" refString="Schotsman, H. D. (1967) Les Callitriches. In: Jovet, P. (Ed.) Flore de France, vol. 1. P. Lechevalier, Paris, 152 pp." type="book" year="1967">Schotsman (1967: 39)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and some populations of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFD08F40BFC56B45C" authority="subsp. truncata" box="[668,973,518,545]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="truncata" subSpecies="truncata">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFD08F40BFC80B45C" box="[668,795,519,545]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">C. truncata</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFCFAF40BFC56B45C" box="[878,973,519,544]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">truncata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<collectingCountry id="F325BBC6FFD17F6AFC7BF40BFBCFB45D" box="[1007,1108,519,545]" name="Morocco" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Morocco</collectingCountry>
(RVL unpublished data) in the combination of stem and leaf scales lacking, flowers solitary, fruit winged and the wing degrading on maturity to leave exposed fibrillae on the margin. 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFE79F442FD2EB414" authorityName="Lansdown &amp; Hassemer" authorityYear="2021" box="[493,693,590,616]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ciliata">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFE79F442FD2EB414" box="[493,693,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Callitriche ciliata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFCD0F443FBE6B414" authorityName="Schotsman" authorityYear="1967" box="[836,1149,590,617]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="truncata" subSpecies="fimbriata">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFCD0F443FC58B414" box="[836,963,591,617]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">C. truncata</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFB81F442FBE6B414" box="[1045,1149,590,616]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">fimbriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and Moroccan populations of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFF32F47EFECAB4F0" box="[166,337,626,652]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="truncata" subSpecies="truncata">
subsp. 
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFF66F47FFECAB4F0" box="[242,337,627,652]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">truncata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in its longer leaves and typically wider fruit. Distribution and morphological differences support the distinction from that species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C328A8DDFFD17F6AFF29F4B6FA89B5AD" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B8DFB56FFD17F6AFF29F4B6FC1EB5D0" blockId="9.[136,1452,482,1589]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFF29F4B6FECAB4A8" bold="true" box="[189,337,698,724]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Description:</emphasis>
—Stem and leaf scales lacking. Leaf bases not connate. Lingulate leaves parallel-sided, 4–19 × 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFF1CF4D2FE8AB485" box="[136,273,734,761]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" metricValueMax="15.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="0.9" valueMax="1.5" valueMin="0.3">0.3–1.5 mm</quantity>
, expanded floating or submerged leaves unknown, apical leaves not forming a floating rosette, terrestrial leaves unknown. Flowers solitary. Bracts lacking. Style initially erect, eventually reflexed, appressed to side of ovary at base, sharplY recurved in apical half, ≤ 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFDCAF52AFD2EB53D" box="[606,693,806,833]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.7" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="2.7">2.7 mm</quantity>
long. Filament straight, ≤ 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFC74F52AFBADB53D" box="[992,1078,806,833]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="0.6">0.6 mm</quantity>
long; anther reniform, 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFAAFF52AFF2FB519" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.65" metricValueMax="4.3" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="0.365" valueMax="0.43" valueMin="0.3">0.30–0.43 mm</quantity>
diameter; pollen colourless. Fruit not strumose, on pedicels ≤ 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFCFFF546FC30B519" box="[875,939,842,869]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="1.0">1 mm</quantity>
long, slightlY wider than long, greYish-brown when mature, 1.2–1.7 × 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFE0AF562FDB3B5F5" box="[414,552,878,905]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="1.9" metricValueMin="1.1" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="1.5" valueMax="1.9" valueMin="1.1">1.1–1.9 mm</quantity>
, wing 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFDE1F562FC82B5F5" box="[629,793,878,905]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.35" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="0.7" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="mm" value="0.135" valueMax="0.2" valueMin="0.07">0.07–0.20 mm</quantity>
wide, initially entire, after ripening reduced to a fringe of the remains of the fibrils which are more or less simple or branched.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8DFB56FFD17F6AFF29F5BAFA89B5AD" blockId="9.[136,1452,482,1589]" box="[189,1298,950,977]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFF29F5BAFEC2B5AC" bold="true" box="[189,345,950,976]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">Illustrations:</emphasis>
— 
<figureCitation id="1309E7D3FFD17F6AFEE1F5BAFE48B5AC" box="[373,467,950,976]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[136,229,1366,1388]" captionTargetBox="[347,1230,205,1317]" captionTargetId="figure-17@3.[337,1251,187,1339]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Fruits of South American Callitriche: a—C. albomarginata, b—C. antarctica, c—C. berteroana, d—C. ciliata, e—C. ciliata showing fibrils, f—C. concinna, g—C. dacryoidea, h—C. deflexa, i—C. ecarinata, j—C. hegelmaieriana, k—C. heterophylla, l—C. heteropoda." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5424746" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5424746/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">
Figure 
<quantity id="4CCA56B3FFD17F6AFE51F5BAFE48B5AC" box="[453,467,950,976]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.54" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" unit="in" value="1.0">1</quantity>
</figureCitation>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA386A7FFD17F6AFE63F5BAFD4DB5AD" author="Bacigalupo, N. M." box="[503,726,950,977]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" pagination="377 - 396" refId="ref28770" refString="Bacigalupo, N. M. (1979 b) El genero Callitriche en la flora argentina. Darwiniana 22: 377 - 396." type="journal article" year="1979">Bacigalupo (1979b)</bibRefCitation>
(as 
<taxonomicName id="4C3280D5FFD17F6AFC91F5BBFBC7B5AD" authority="Gussone [1826: 4]" authorityName="Gussone" authorityPageNumber="4" authorityYear="1826" box="[773,1116,950,977]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Callitriche" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="truncata">
<emphasis id="B9462744FFD17F6AFC91F5BBFC1FB5AC" box="[773,900,951,977]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="94">C. truncata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFA386A7FFD17F6AFC1FF5BAFBC7B5AD" author="Gussone, J." box="[907,1116,950,977]" pageId="9" pageNumber="94" refId="ref29179" refString="Gussone, J. (1826) Plantae rariores. Regia Typographia, Naples, 401 pp., 66 plates." type="book" year="1826">Gussone [1826: 4]</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
); 
